::Havoc::

Havoc grits his teeth as Demolition gets him into a wrestling pin, 
feeling his leg being stretched further than it was meant to. He 
reaches to the side, taking the sword he had dropped during the fall 
and swinging it as hard as he could at Demolition's head.
